| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4958 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3bdd080c-4bdb-5966-b9f5-62a6f85eebbb"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
